{"orig":"/Users/kalaverin/src/lang/nim/lib/pure/streamwrapper.nim","nimble":"stdlib","moduleDescription":"<p>This module implements stream wrapper.</p>\n<p><strong>Since</strong> version 1.2.</p>\n","entries":[{"name":"PipeOutStream","type":"skType","line":21,"col":20,"code":"PipeOutStream[T] = ref object of T"},{"name":"newPipeOutStream","type":"skProc","line":89,"col":0,"code":"proc newPipeOutStream[T](s: sink (ref T)): owned PipeOutStream[T]","signature":{"return":"owned PipeOutStream[T]","arguments":[{"name":"s","type":"sink (ref T)"}],"genericParams":[{"name":"T"}]},"description":"<p>Wrap pipe for reading with PipeOutStream so that you can use peek* procs and generate runtime error when setPosition/getPosition is called or write operation is performed.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<p><pre class=\"listing\"><span class=\"Keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">std</span><span class=\"Operator\">/</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"Identifier\">osproc</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">streamwrapper</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"Keyword\">var</span>\n  <span class=\"Identifier\">p</span> <span class=\"Operator\">=</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">startProcess</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Identifier\">exePath</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"Identifier\">outStream</span> <span class=\"Operator\">=</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">p</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">outputStream</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">newPipeOutStream</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"Identifier\">echo</span> <span class=\"Identifier\">outStream</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">peekChar</span>\n<span class=\"Identifier\">p</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">close</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span></pre></p>\n"}]}